msgctxt "dn15:24.4"
msgid "Tatrānanda, yo so rūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti."
msgstr "Now, take those who describe the self as physical and infinite …"

msgctxt "dn15:24.5"
msgid "Etarahi vā so rūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti, tattha bhāviṃ vā so rūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti, ‘atathaṃ vā pana santaṃ tathattāya upakappessāmī’ti iti vā panassa hoti."
msgstr ""

