msgctxt "dn15:24.10"
msgid "Tatrānanda, yo so arūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti."
msgstr "formless and infinite."

msgctxt "dn15:24.11"
msgid "Etarahi vā so arūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti, tattha bhāviṃ vā so arūpiṃ anantaṃ attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti, ‘atathaṃ vā pana santaṃ tathattāya upakappessāmī’ti iti vā panassa hoti."
msgstr "They describe the self as formless and infinite in the present; or in some future life; or else they think: ‘Though it is not like that, I will ensure it is provided with what it needs to become like that.’"

msgctxt "dn15:24.12"
msgid "Evaṃ santaṃ kho, ānanda, arūpiṃ anantattānudiṭṭhi anusetīti iccālaṃ vacanāya."
msgstr "This being so, it’s appropriate to say that a view of self as formless and infinite underlies them."

msgctxt "dn15:24.13"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, ānanda, attānaṃ paññapento paññapeti."
msgstr "That’s how those who describe the self describe it."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn15:24.14"
msgid "3. Naattapaññatti"
msgstr "3. Not Describing the Self"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36"></a>
msgctxt "dn15:25.1"
msgid "Kittāvatā ca, ānanda, attānaṃ na paññapento na paññapeti?"
msgstr "How do those who don’t describe the self not describe it?"

msgctxt "dn15:25.2"
msgid "Rūpiṃ vā hi, ānanda, parittaṃ attānaṃ na paññapento na paññapeti:"
msgstr "They don’t describe it as physical and limited …"

msgctxt "dn15:25.3"
msgid "‘rūpī me paritto attā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn15:25.4"
msgid "Rūpiṃ vā hi, ānanda, anantaṃ attānaṃ na paññapento na paññapeti:"
msgstr "physical and infinite …"

msgctxt "dn15:25.5"
msgid "‘rūpī me ananto attā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn15:25.6"
msgid "Arūpiṃ vā hi, ānanda, parittaṃ attānaṃ na paññapento na paññapeti:"
msgstr "formless and limited …"

msgctxt "dn15:25.7"
msgid "‘arūpī me paritto attā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn15:25.8"
msgid "Arūpiṃ vā hi, ānanda, anantaṃ attānaṃ na paññapento na paññapeti:"
msgstr "formless and infinite:"

msgctxt "dn15:25.9"
msgid "‘arūpī me ananto attā’ti."
msgstr "‘My self is formless and infinite.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc37"></a>
